works.description:
A Russian entity has copied an old version of the website of the Seattle-area based orchestra Northwest Sinfonietta and published it on the domain nwsinfonietta.com.

The correct domain name of the orchestra is nwsinfonietta.org or northwestsinfonietta.org (which is currently in development).  
The domain contact info for both correct domains is Neil Birnbaum, the executive director of the organization.  He can be called at (253) 383-5344 for verification.
